---
title: Open-Faced Prosciutto & Jam Sandwiches with Ricotta & Arugula
description: The only thing better than a really great sandwich is one that takes just minutes to prepare! Yep, all you have to do is assemble and dig in. This Really Great Sandwich has crusty sourdough bread, sweet peach jam, salty prosciutto, creamy fresh ricotta, and a tangle of lemon-kissed, peppery arugula. All dressed up, this open-faced beauty looks fancy enough to approach with a knife-and-fork, but it’s a sandwich, so get in there with your hands, maybe with your pinkies up.
